TopicTitle: Tech tree trouble with docking ports

Articles.Content:
Docking is one of the first skills and goals in KSP.

You want to practice this skill before going to the mun.

Lots of fun to be had 

Sadly the docking ports have been switched around.

We now get the bigger Clamp O tron we can't us for anything right now.

So the Junior needs to be first .

We need to have our Kermini missions Nate!
